name: Enable Technology
overview:
A Kansas City website design firm working for Small and Medium Business (SMB), non profits and local governments. Provide complete websites and wide array of related services at reasonable rates.

Focused on small business as a full service provider for all internet related needs, including custom website development, programming, integration, social media marketing, local search optimization and web/print graphics design and printing services.

Offers many advanced technologies that are often unattainable by local business; such as data conversion, analytics and detailed data analysis using a variety of open source tools.
